                           \n\n\n  (Page 2 of 3)                                                                                                     \n\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n\n  Name:                                                                                                             \n\n\n──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n\n  1. Career Related to Design and Construction, etc.                                                                \n\n\n────────┬───────────────────────┬─────────┬─────────┬─────\n\n\n  Period of     │Name of Project                               │Area of           │Jobs Assigned     │Remarks   \n\n\n  Participation │                                              │Expertise         │                  │          \n\n\n  (Date of      ├───────────┬───────────┼─────────┼─────────┤          \n\n\n  Recognition)  │Project Owner         │Category of           │Specialty in the  │Position          │          \n\n\n                │                      │Construction Works    │Area              │                  │          \n\n\n                ├───────────┴───────────┼─────────┼─────────┤          \n\n\n                │Summary of Construction works(Services)       │Level of          │Construction Cost │          \n\n\n                │                                              │Responsibility    │(Service Fee)     │          \n\n\n                │                                              │                  │(Millions in KRW) │          \n\n\n                ├───────────┬───────────┼─────────┼─────────┤          \n\n\n                │Construction Methods  │Convergence/          │New Technologies  │Types of          │          \n\n\n                │Applied               │Integration           │Applied           │Facilities        │          \n\n\n                │                      │Technologies Applied  │                  │                  │          \n\n\n───